    {
      "id": "ArfmVmpU3kpKEKDMzW1nZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -782.395230980392,
      "y": 4705.703770398857,
      "width": 1842.6177236066642,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6z",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 493628744,
      "version": 258,
      "versionNonce": 1642190648,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1768572608729,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Inference request path: client → gateway → tenant LB → inference service/runtime → response, Strict Tenant Isolation\n2. Admission/budget decision path: api gateway(AuthN) -> cache(AuthZ+Budget)(materialized view, not authoritative), Fail-Closed Budget Enforcement\n3. Desired state write: CP writes desired state + immutable version → emits reconcile event → reconciler applies to serving plane → status update, Immutable Promotion History\n4. Approval/promotion: Version Uploaded to Storage for approval -> RDBMS Linked Pending -> AuthZ user Approval/Reject Link ->  <Desired state write>, Explicit Promotion Gate\n5. Reconciliation/apply: scheduled reconciliation -> reconciler applies to serving plane → status update, Immutable Promotion History\n6. Observability + telemetry emission: structured inference metadata + optional sampled/redacted payloads under policy, Telemetry data is not in the Hot Path\n7. Observability/status update surfaces: Status/usage query path: client → CP APIs → authoritative store → response\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Inference request path: client → gateway → tenant LB → inference service/runtime → response, Strict Tenant Isolation\n2. Admission/budget decision path: api gateway(AuthN) -> cache(AuthZ+Budget)(materialized view, not authoritative), Fail-Closed Budget Enforcement\n3. Desired state write: CP writes desired state + immutable version → emits reconcile event → reconciler applies to serving plane → status update, Immutable Promotion History\n4. Approval/promotion: Version Uploaded to Storage for approval -> RDBMS Linked Pending -> AuthZ user Approval/Reject Link ->  <Desired state write>, Explicit Promotion Gate\n5. Reconciliation/apply: scheduled reconciliation -> reconciler applies to serving plane → status update, Immutable Promotion History\n6. Observability + telemetry emission: structured inference metadata + optional sampled/redacted payloads under policy, Telemetry data is not in the Hot Path\n7. Observability/status update surfaces: Status/usage query path: client → CP APIs → authoritative store → response\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZUEMepKbieSPM2CxQTusx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 84.41200926186161,
      "y": 213.65172242363133,
